description:
This is a 21 minute workout called 'Advanced HIIT Row ' from the channel Aisyah Rafaee.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor rowing.
It's suitable for Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Nightclub Workout vibe.
The The Warrior Workout vibe means Unleash your inner beast. Sweat-dripping, heart-pounding, primal energy. This is especially good for Days when you want to destroy stress and feel invincible. The The Nightclub Workout vibe means Lights down, music up, full-body euphoria. This is especially good for When you want to move like no oneâ€™s watching and feel amazing..
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Extreme and Challenging.

Original workout description: Reach high rhythms at maximum effort with Aisyah and Nick as you listen to an all female artist playlist and think of your most influential, female athletes.
